oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Brand on My Heart by Willie Nelson and Hank Snow
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording is of the album Brand on My Heart, performed by Willie Nelson (musician) and Hank Snow (musician). The recordings are from an unidentified date. The album is produced by Chips Moman and engineered by David Cherry.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Willie Nelson; Hank Snow
